}\" href=\"${navItem.getRegularURL()!\"\"}\" ${navItem.getTarget()}>${htmlUtil.escape(navItem.getName())}</a>\n					<#else>\n						${htmlUtil.escape(navItem.getName())}\n					</#if>\n\n					<#if includeAllChildNavItems || navItem.isInNavigation(branchNavItems)>\n						<@buildNavigation\n							branchNavItems=branchNavItems\n							cssClass=cssClass\n							displayDepth=displayDepth\n							includeAllChildNavItems=includeAllChildNavItems\n							navItemLevel=(navItemLevel + 1)\n							navItems=navItem.getChildren()\n						/>\n					</#if>\n				</li>\n			</#list>\n		</ul>\n	</#if>\n</#macro>',0,20120,NULL,'2017-04-18 12:51:58.785000'),(29049,20160,20116,20120,NULL,'2017-04-18 12:51:58.985000',29016,0,29047,'1.0','<?xml version=\'1.0\' encoding=\'UTF-8\'?><root available-locales=\"en_US,zh_CN,es_ES,ja_JP,nl_NL,hu_HU,pt_BR,de_DE,iw_IL,fi_FI,ca_ES,fr_FR,\" default-locale=\"en_US\"><Name language-id=\"zh_CN\">拆分下拉菜单按钮</Name><Name language-id=\"es_ES\">Botón de división de menús desplegables</Name><Name language-id=\"ja_JP\">分割ボタンドロップダウン</Name><Name language-id=\"nl_NL\">Split Button Dropdowns</Name><Name language-id=\"hu_HU\">Osztó gomb legördülők</Name><Name language-id=\"pt_BR\">Botões Suspensos Separados</Name><Name language-id=\"de_DE\">Split-Button-Dropdowns</Name><Name language-id=\"iw_IL\">תיבות נפתחות עם כפתור מפוצל</Name><Name language-id=\"fi_FI\">Jaettu pudotuslistanappi</Name><Name language-id=\"ca_ES\">Menús desplegables amb botó de divisió</Name><Name language-id=\"fr_FR\">Bouton séparer de listes déroulantes</Name><Name language-id=\"en_US\">Split Button Dropdowns</Name></root>','<?xml version=\'1.0\' encoding=\'UTF-8\'?><root available-locales=\"en_US,zh_CN,es_ES,ja_JP,nl_NL,hu_HU,pt_BR,de_DE,iw_IL,fi_FI,ca_ES,fr_FR,\" default-locale=\"en_US\"><Description language-id=\"zh_CN\">显示有Bootstrap按钮的下拉式导航菜单。</Description><Description language-id=\"es_ES\">Displays a dropdown navigation menu with root menu items shown as buttons.</Description><Description language-